      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera. Finished in a deep Seal Grey Metallic with a flawless Graphite Grey leather interior, this vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint remains original and maintains a mirror-like finish, protected by a recent professional ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin is impeccable\u2014the leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left Stuttgart. Mechanically, this 911 is beyond reproach. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed, and it comes with a complete binder of service records documenting every oil change and inspection. With incredibly low mileage and a smooth-shifting 6-speed manual transmission, it drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car. Included are the original window sticker, two keys, and all factory manuals. This is a collector-grade example suited for the most discerning enthusiast.",
